#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/system.rst:2 a5faac1ea329476ab4cbc95c271c75d9
msgid "系统"
msgstr "System"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/system.rst:17 801978795a174baba953c5ee1afc1697
msgid "CPU架构，运行频率以及RAM"
msgstr "CPU architecture, operating frequency, and RAM"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/system.rst:18 d82241fbaf63460c97b2ba082590bd64
msgid "BL602是基于RISC-V处理器芯片，最高运行频率是160MHz,特殊情况下允许超频到192M，芯片可用RAM。"
msgstr "BL602 is based on a RISC-V processor chip. Its maximum operating frequency is 160 MHz; in special cases, it can be overclocked to 192 MHz. The chip has usable RAM."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/system.rst:21 6095716f34cc4d49b3d3b7db0b689fbb
msgid "模组从上电到运行程序最快需要多长时间？"
msgstr "What is the shortest time required for the module to run the program after power-on?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/system.rst:22 eca2b47d8c154402b35062721bb7a932
msgid "约3ms。"
msgstr "About 3 ms."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/system.rst:25 4bfa86dfe9a74b20a406822dd68b70dc
msgid "模组掉电的时候，数据存储在哪里？"
msgstr "Where is data stored when the module is powered off?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/system.rst:26 0197277e069f4def9a6baa00e85a7a8b
msgid "完全掉电时，芯片内ram上的数据均会丢失。PDS、HBN模式不同level下ram区域掉电情况各不相同，需要case by case。"
msgstr "When power is completely cut off, all data in the chip’s internal RAM will be lost. In PDS and HBN modes, the RAM power-down status varies depending on different levels and needs to be analyzed case by case."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/system.rst:29 a74e33fbd4a44d5f8b592af0264ad1a5
msgid "为什么模块默认支持Cli串口通讯，在哪设置不开启这个选型？"
msgstr "Why does the module support CLI serial communication by default, and where can this option be disabled?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/system.rst:30 e19dda57e80b4be2915ce76173090d49
msgid "我们移植了命令行交互工具cli（command-line interface），已经将其移植到我们到系统中，在对应的工程目录的 proj_config.mk 文件把 CONFIG_SYS_AOS_CLI_ENABLE:=0，如果没有，则添加这个设置。"
msgstr "We have ported the command-line interaction tool CLI (command-line interface) into the system. To disable it, set the following in the proj_config.mk file under the corresponding project directory: CONFIG_SYS_AOS_CLI_ENABLE:=0. If this setting does not exist, add it."

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/system.rst:33 e04d591f4c6448e0a6d39a228528feee
msgid "为什么我写的组件或代码，无法开启LOG打印日志？"
msgstr "Why can't the component or code I wrote enable LOG printing?"

#: ../../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/system.rst:34 a0962092d36d4490b2c8f7dd204c0b07
msgid "日志管理组件blog开关需在相应的 proj_config.mk 文件目录下，LOG_ENABLED_COMPONENTS配置上增加对应组件的名字 例如这里需要增加blog_testa blog_testb blog_testc 的日志输出：LOG_ENABLED_COMPONENTS:=blog_testa blog_testb blog_testc 其他组件默认关闭，组件名字就是其文件夹名字。"
msgstr "The switch for the log management component blog must be configured in the corresponding proj_config.mk file directory. Add the corresponding component names to LOG_ENABLED_COMPONENTS. For example, to enable log output for blog_testa, blog_testb, and blog_testc, configure: LOG_ENABLED_COMPONENTS:=blog_testa blog_testb blog_testc. Other components are disabled by default. The component name is the same as its folder name."

#~ msgid ":link_to_translation:`en:[English]`"
#~ msgstr ""
